03 Jul 2017 01:51:33 : Mareep Pasture, stats, 8RavenPhoenix8#9848, Name - Raven (Flaafy)
Gender - Female
Species - Electric Wool Pokemon
Type - Electric/Dark
Level - 25
Ability - Super Luck 
Moves - Charge, Electro ball, Haze, Sucker punch
Nature - Quiet
Stats - HP 70, Attack 55, Defense 60, Sp. Attack 85, Sp. Defense 55, Speed 45 (total - 310)
Height - 2'09" 
Weight - 28.3 lbs.
Egg Group - Field, Monster, Flying

Trivia - Raven is a crossbreed between an Ampharos and a Honchkrow. Normally, this either wouldn't work or produce an ordinary Mareep, however, her father 'knew a guy who knew a guy' and so on and so forth who could create a child from both of their DNA, creating Raven.
Trivia - Raven has feathers just in front of her horns. They don't serve any purpose really, but she can easily tell which way the wind is blowing, often to her dismay. They do not shed, and they change with her as she evolves.
Trivia - Raven's wool is less wooly than that of most Flaafy. It has a softer, downier texture, although it can hold electricity just the same.
Trivia: Due to her father being a Honckrow, not only is Raven part dark type, but she can learn some moves of a Murkrow/Honchkrow. She also is in a third egg group, Flying, and has the ability Super Luck.
